{"items":[{"id":"7045","user":{"id":"148883","nickname":"活动喵","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/nemo/ryc-BqCbv.jpeg","subject_id":228,"work_shop_name":"编程猫官方","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":2,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>楼上正解，点赞；</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>另外补充一下，笔和橡皮擦切换的思路：</p>\n<p>添加一个新角色“切换按钮”；</p>\n<p>添加一个全局变量A；添加脚本，游戏开始时设置A值为0；</p>\n<p>给“切换按钮”，添加脚本，当角色被点击时，判断A值，为0时+1，否则-1；</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>修改角色“画笔”的脚本，在主流程处（移到鼠标，鼠标按下落笔，否则抬笔）套一个重复判断，如果A值为0，执行主流程，否则移到固定位置。</p>\n<p>新建角色“橡皮擦”，复制修改后的“画笔”的主流程的脚本，在橡皮擦角色下粘贴，A值判断为1，画笔颜色更改为背景色。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>以上仅供参考~<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/5.gif\"></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":3,"updated_at":1478977097,"created_at":1478977097,"earliest_comments":[{"id":"450646","user":{"id":"2188300","nickname":"Molong","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"捕捉活动喵","created_at":1588736730},{"id":"1369150","user":{"id":"1638393223","nickname":"双鱼之下","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTYzODM5MzIyM18xNjM4MzkzMjIzXzE2NDMwMTU3NDQxMDNfZDllZGQ2YjY.jpeg","subject_id":10395,"work_shop_name":"四了","work_shop_level":1,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"捉!","created_at":1643627475},{"id":"1390486","user":{"id":"8808580","nickname":"尖端放电","avatar_url":"https://creation.bcmcdn.com//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfODgwODU4MF8wXzE3MjQyMDI1Njk2MjFfSm9nTzk2NGo=.jpg","subject_id":7437,"work_shop_name":"王者工作室","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"catch！","created_at":1646219828}]},{"id":"1298099","user":{"id":"9788710","nickname":"蒙大拿州的角龙","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfOTc4ODcxMF85Nzg4NzEwXzE2NzI5NzUwMzU4NT